'''''Andrews High School''''' (AHS) in [[Andrews, North Carolina|Andrews]], [[North Carolina]] serves grades 9-12 and is one of only three high schools in the [[Cherokee_County_(North_Carolina)_School_District|Cherokee County School District]]. As of 2007 it had an active enrollment of 279 students and a full time teaching staff of 27 teachers giving an average of 11 students per teacher.<ref>[http://cherokeecounty.nc.schoolwebpages.com/education/components/scdirectory/default.php?sectiondetailid=423& Andrews High - Staff<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref><ref>[http://www.psk12.com/rating/USindivphp/SchID_300376_year_2007.html Andrews,High School,Cherokee County, North Carolina<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>
==Athletics== ===Sports Teams=== Football, track ===Facilities=== Gym, weight-room, showers, track
